						               													<description>This edition puts all of the game play extras in one big, foil-stamped box:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Base Game&amp;#10;     Big Rig and the Final 5&amp;#10;     Carnage at Devil's Run&amp;#10;     Choppe Shoppe&amp;#10;     Extra Ammo&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Plus:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Custom plastic insert&amp;#10;     Stretch Goals&amp;#10;     Exclusive Crew Leader Em Berco&amp;#10;     Exclusive mini-expansion German Engineering&amp;#10;     Exclusive consolidated rulebook&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;(From update #13):&amp;#10;Maximum Chrome includes the base game and all three expansions: ''Big Rig &amp;amp; the Final 5'', ''Carnage at Devil's Run'', and ''Choppe Shoppe''. It includes the ''Extra Ammo'' mini-expansion pack. It also includes three items only available in this edition. The German Engineering mini-expansion offers a new way to play, replacing the movement and shooting dice with a hand of cards. The Em Berco crew leader mixes features from Choppe Shoppe and Carnage for a blazing good time. And you also get a consolidated rulebook that incorporates the rules for all the game content in one place with appropriate cross-references for ease of use. And it all comes stored in a custom plastic insert to hold everything in place and a foil-stamped box that looks extra swanky.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Maximum Chrome will not be going into retail distribution.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Addendum: It's been confirmed the insert will be card-sleeve-friendly.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
